== Easter Eggs ==

=== Developer's Room ===
* Beat Lavos at the very beginning of New Game+
* Access a room where you can speak with the development team

=== Gonzales ===
* A friendly robot enemy in Lab 32
* Can be fought repeatedly for easy Tech Points

=== Nu Sprites ===
* Nu creatures appear throughout the game with hints and secrets
* One in the Hunting Range drops a powerful accessory

== Tips ==

'''Farming:'''
* Black Omen can be completed in each time period for triple rewards
* Geno Dome enemies drop good equipment
* Death Peak has respawning fights

'''Speed Running:'''
* Skip optional sidequests for faster completion
* The bucket in End of Time allows early Lavos access
* Certain glitches allow sequence breaks

